# $Id: README,v 1.2 2002/05/01 12:52:48 rowan Exp $

In order to install and use this package you will need Perl version
5.004 or better, mod_perl and Mail::IMAPClient. Installation as usual:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Copyright 2002, John "Rowan" Littell <littejo@earlham.edu>

The Apache::AuthenIMAPClient module is free software; you can
redistribute it and/or modify it under the same terms as Perl itself.
